727431f-b.title: Queens: Metropolitan Avenue - 78th Street
727431f-b.text:
Metropoiitan Avenue, north side, west of 78th Street, showing
in three views in order from fore to hackground the Abraham Folk
blaclsmith shop and house, a doubie two story structure, J. Schneider's
Middle Village Hoteu, and the M.E. Church of Newtown.
October 1923
View 2:1922
View 3:Fehruary 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
